Vſe 1. This doctrine ſerueth to confute, and ouerthrow the Popiſh Maſſe, wherein the Prieſt would repreſent Chriſt vnto the People: for this Sacrament is onely ordained of God, as a liuely meanes to repreſent
Chriſt, and to ſhew forth his death till he come, but yet they are not contented with this liuely repreſentation of Chriſ • exhibited, but they haue brought in three more repreſentations, and ſo make foure in all;
